item.title: By: Ben
item.dc:creator: Ben
item.description: Thanks! Believe it or not, I was having issues writing posts sometimes because I would sit there thinking what I would title things. And then next thing you know I've titled a post something I would probably have titled an article. Classifying these types of rants / posts as simple Journal Entries should make for much fluid blogging. Appreciate the support as always man! It's definitely much needed as I start everything back up!
item.content:encoded:
